          "description": "Per-cluster snapshot at the end of the selected time range. The Retention column estimates how many days the local on-disk audit log covers given the standard --audit-log-maxbackup=30 \u00d7 --audit-log-maxsize=100MB rotation (9 GB of rotated logs per cluster across 3 control-plane nodes, divided by the cluster's daily write rate).",
